# UML Class Diagram (Text Representation)

Person
 ├── Passenger
 └── Driver

Automobile (interface)
 └── Vehicle
      ├── Combi
      └── Taxi

Routecombi
 └── Tripcombi
      └── Bookingcombi

Routetaxi
 └── Triptaxi
      └── Bookingtaxi

Relationships:
- Vehicle HAS-A Driver
- Tripcombi HAS-A Routecombi and Combi
- Triptaxi HAS-A Routetaxi and Taxi
- Bookingcombi HAS-A Passenger and Tripcombi
- Bookingtaxi HAS-A Passenger and Triptaxi

